Conclusion

This project demonstrates how modern recommendation systems evolve beyond simple text matching. By combining classical NLP (TF-IDF) with transformer-based embeddings, the system achieves a more human-like understanding 
of movie similarity.

It reflects how real-world AI systems operate — blending multiple models to improve accuracy, interpretability, and user experience.

